'''中國－巴巴多斯關係'''（{{lang-en|China–Barbados relations}}），是指[[中華人民共和國|中華人民共和國]]和[[巴巴多斯|巴巴多斯]]之間的雙邊關係。巴巴多斯独立后，曾在1967年与中华民国建交，直到1977年断交，之后巴巴多斯於1977年5月30日与中华人民共和国建交<ref name="CEIB">{{cite web |url=http://bb.chineseembassy.org/eng/zbgx/t261184.htm |title=Summary of China-Barbados Bilateral Relations |author=Ambassador |date=30 May 2008 |publisher=Embassy of the People's Republic of China: Barbados |location=Bridgetown, Barbados |trans_title= |deadurl=no |accessdate=16 January 2012 |quote= |ref= |separator= |postscript= |archive-date=2014-01-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140102191143/http://bb.chineseembassy.org/eng/zbgx/t261184.htm }}</ref>，中國一直向巴巴多斯提供援助，例如協助建設{{link-en|加菲爾德·疏巴斯體育館|Garfield Sobers Gymnasium}}等項目。自2004年起，中國開始向欲前往巴巴多斯的公民發出ADS签证<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.chinatraveltrends.com/2009/08/approved-destination-status/|title=List of Chinese countries with ADS status|authorlink=|publisher=[[China_Travel_Trends|China Travel Trends]]|at=|date=6 August 2009|trans_title=|deadurl=yes|quote=([http://www.chinatraveltrends.com/wp-content/uploads/2009/09/ADS-countries-and-territories.pdf list])|ref=|separator=|postscript=|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110103150756/http://www.chinatraveltrends.com/2009/08/approved-destination-status/|archivedate=2011年1月3日|accessdate=2014年7月15日}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |title=What China Means for Caribbean Tourism |author=Caribbean Journal staff |url=http://www.caribjournal.com/2011/12/17/what-china-could-mean-to-caribbean-tourism/ |agency=Caribbean Journal |date=17 December 2011 |at= |accessdate=30 September 2012 |quote= |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120812060049/http://www.caribjournal.com/2011/12/17/what-china-could-mean-to-caribbean-tourism/ |archivedate=2012-08-12 |deadurl=no |ref= }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |title=Chinese tourism remains a goal |first=A. |last=N. |url=http://www.barbadosadvocate.com/newsitem.asp?more=local&NewsID=25056 |newspaper=[[Barbados_Advocate|Barbados Advocate]] |date=1 June 2012 |accessdate=30 September 2012 |quote= |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140718102047/http://www.barbadosadvocate.com/newsitem.asp?more=local&NewsID=25056 |archivedate=2014-07-18 |deadurl=yes |ref= }}</ref>。2008年[[汶川大地震|汶川大地震]]後，[[巴巴多斯總理|巴巴多斯總理]][[戴維·湯普森|戴維·湯普森]]前往中國大使館，在弔唁冊上親筆簽字<ref>[http://bb.china-embassy.org/eng/xwdt/t460379.htm Prime Minister David Thompson signed condolence book] {{Wayback|url=http://bb.china-embassy.org/eng/xwdt/t460379.htm |date=20120222102406 }}, 21 May 2008</ref>。

目前，中國駐巴巴多斯大使館位於[[基督城教區_(巴巴多斯)|基督城教區]]<ref>{{cite news |title=China marks 63 years |first=A. |last=N. |authorlink= |url=http://www.barbadosadvocate.com/newsitem.asp?more=local&NewsID=27071 |format= |agency= |newspaper=[[Barbados_Advocate|Barbados Advocate]] |publisher= |location= |date=28 September 2012 |at= |accessdate=29 September 2012 |language= |quote=“Since I assumed my post as the Chinese Ambassador April this year, I have been much impressed by the sound friendship between our two countries and two peoples, as well as the great potential for future development,” Ambassador Xu Hong stated. |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131027115600/http://www.barbadosadvocate.com/newsitem.asp?more=local&NewsID=27071 |archivedate=2013-10-27 |deadurl=yes |ref= }}</ref>，而大使為王克；巴巴多斯駐中國大使館則位於[[北京|北京]]，大使為{{link-en|桑迪福德|Lloyd Erskine Sandiford}}<ref name="BAIC">{{cite web|title=Chinese president accepts credentials from five new ambassadors|publisher=Xinhua News Agency|date=3 March 2010|accessdate=17 January 2012|url=http://news.xinhuanet.com/english2010/china/2010-03/03/c_13195842.htm|archive-date=2010-03-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100307062717/http://news.xinhuanet.com/english2010/china/2010-03/03/c_13195842.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。中國和巴巴多斯同是[[聯合國|聯合國]]、[[加勒比開發銀行|加勒比開發銀行]]和[[77國集團|77國集團]]的成員。

2017年3月24日，中華人民共和国与巴巴多斯签订普通护照互免签证协议<ref>{{Cite web |title=中国与巴巴多斯政府签署互免持普通护照人员签证协定 |url=http://cs.mfa.gov.cn/gyls/lsgz/lqbb/t1449064.shtml |accessdate=2017-03-25 |author=中国驻巴巴多斯大使馆 |publisher=中国领事服务网 |archive-date=2019-01-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190124021338/http://cs.mfa.gov.cn/gyls/lsgz/lqbb/t1449064.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>，并于同年6月1日生效<ref>{{Cite web |title=关于中国与巴巴多斯互免持普通护照人员签证协定生效通知 |url=http://bb.chineseembassy.org/chn/xwdt/t1461968.htm |accessdate=2017-05-16 |author=中国驻巴巴多斯大使馆 |publisher=中国驻巴巴多斯大使馆 |archive-date=2017-06-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170620044938/http://bb.chineseembassy.org/chn/xwdt/t1461968.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>

== 經貿關係 ==
在1999年，中國到巴巴多斯的出口總額為​​2,035,000[[美元|美元]]，而巴巴多斯到中國的出口總額為13,000美元；2005年，中國到巴巴多斯的出口總額為1,919萬美元，而巴巴多斯到中國的出口總額為211000美元<ref name="CEIB" />。中巴兩國簽署了[[租稅協定|租稅協定]]及相互促進和保護投資條約。中國政府是以巴巴多斯為基礎的加勒比開發銀行的主要得益者<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.caribank.org/titanweb/cdb/webcms.nsf/AllDoc/E3B470BE4AD4B5EF8725733700799FD6?OpenDocument |title=Caribbean Development Bank (CDB): Non-Regional Members |accessdate=2014-07-15 |archive-date=2012-03-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120330194210/http://www.caribank.org/titanweb/cdb/webcms.nsf/AllDoc/E3B470BE4AD4B5EF8725733700799FD6?OpenDocument |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |title=Closer cooperation likely between China and Barbados |author=Staff writers |url=http://www.caribbeannetnews.com/news-14318--26-26--.html |newspaper=CaribbeanNetNews.com |date=17 February 2009 |accessdate=10 September 2009 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090505132748/http://www.caribbeannetnews.com/news-14318--26-26--.html |archivedate=2009-05-05 }}</ref>。

2004年，中國一些企業開始介入巴巴多斯建築業，包括[[中國建築工程總公司|中國建築工程總公司]]<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.cscec.com.cn/english/co_jigoushezhi.htm#4 |title=China State Construction Engineering Corporation's organizations |accessdate=2014-07-15 |archive-date=2010-07-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100715193035/http://www.cscec.com.cn/english/co_jigoushezhi.htm#4 |dead-url=no }}</ref>和[[ChinaDOS建築有限公司|ChinaDOS建築有限公司]]<ref>[http://www.caipo.gov.bb/search/search.php Registered company search] {{Wayback|url=http://www.caipo.gov.bb/search/search.php |date=20100502074855 }} – By the Corporate Affairs and Intellectual Property Office in Barbados</ref>，在巴巴多斯完成了一批建設項目。2008年8月，中國官員和以巴巴多斯為基礎的[[加勒比出口|加勒比出口]]（[[英語|英語]]：{{lang|en|Caribbean Export}}）簽署了一項協議，以增強加勒比地區到中國的出口市場的可容性<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.barbadosadvocate.com/newsitem.asp?more=business&NewsID=5302 |title=Chinese agreement to be signed with Caribbean Export |accessdate=4 August 2009 |first=J |last=B |date=5 August 2009 |work=[[Barbados_Advocate|The Barbados Advocate]] |quote= |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120215152448/http://www.barbadosadvocate.com/newsitem.asp?more=business&NewsID=5302 |archivedate=2012年2月15日 }}</ref>。

== 軍政關係 ==
2006年10月，巴巴多斯政府被發現沒有與[[美軍|美軍]]簽署{{link-en|第98條協定|United States and the International Criminal Court#Article 98 Agreements}}，以豁免美方人員受國際刑事法院的審訊，並因而被美國制裁，中國政府便向巴巴多斯提供了財政援助<ref name="NationNews">{{cite news |url=http://www.nationnews.com/story/296599452302703.php |title=US calls off Barbados ban |accessdate=24 October 2008 |first=Tony |last=Best |date=24 October 2008 |work=[[The_Daily_Nation_(Barbados)|Nation Newspaper]] |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070927185950/http://www.nationnews.com/story/296599452302703.php |archivedate=2007-09-27 |quote= |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。

於2009年，兩國的軍事單位同意加強軍事合作<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.barbadosadvocate.com/newsitem.asp?more=local&NewsID=7317 |title=Chinese and BDF working together |accessdate=2014-07-15 |archive-date=2012-02-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120226124636/http://www.barbadosadvocate.com/newsitem.asp?more=local&NewsID=7317 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.nationnews.com/news/local/chinese-tour-hmbs-copy-for-web |title=Chinese aid for BDF |accessdate=2014-07-15 |archive-date=2009-11-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20091117191544/http://www.nationnews.com/news/local/chinese-tour-hmbs-copy-for-web |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

